# Animated Portfolio Website

A modern, animated portfolio website built with React, Framer Motion, and Tailwind CSS. Showcasing a beautiful dark-themed design with smooth animations and interactive components.

## Features

- **Animated Hero Section** – Smooth entrance animations with scrolling indicator
- **Responsive Design** – Fully responsive layout that works on all devices
- **Dark Theme** – Elegant dark gradient background with purple accents
- **Smooth Animations** – Framer Motion powered animations throughout
- **Component Library** – Built with Radix UI and shadcn/ui components
- **Modern Styling** – Tailwind CSS for rapid, maintainable styling
- **Interactive Elements** – Hover effects and transitions on interactive components

## Sections

- **Hero** – Eye-catching introduction with profile image and call-to-action buttons
- **About** – Personal background and professional information
- **Projects** – Showcase of work and achievements
- **Skills** – Technical expertise and proficiencies
- **Contact** – Contact form and social links

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: React 18
- **Build Tool**: Vite
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Component Library**: Radix UI, shadcn/ui
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **UI Icons**: Lucide React
- **Type Safety**: TypeScript
- **Language**: JavaScript/TypeScript

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Node.js (v16 or higher)
- npm or yarn

